    <string name="missing_sensor_dialog_text" translation_description="Dialog message shown when the device appears to be missing the compass or accelerometer sensors needed for auto mode">
    To automatically follow the stars as you move, Sky Map needs a built-in compass and accelerometer. It looks like your device is missing one of these.
        \nDon\'t worry! You can still explore the universe in Manual Mode. Just use your fingers to drag, rotate, and zoom around the night sky at your own pace.
    </string>
